verbose_text: Consistent with the results of our previous study, we found that arnebin-1 had no noticeable effect on cell viability and proliferation (as no changes were observed in PCNA expression), as evaluated by MTT assay in the test range, but had a synergistic effect with VEGF in that it promoted HUVEC proliferation (XREF_FIG).
evidence: VEGF in that it promoted HUVEC proliferation
